# Environment Rules

- This is a standalone Expo app running on Windows.
- ALWAYS use Windows-compatible command execution paths if native wrappers fail.
- DO NOT attempt to install new linting or formatting packages automatically.
- If a global cache access error occurs (e.g., in C:\Users\radel\), abort the check instantly rather than trying to request permissions or loop through shims.
- Prioritize code changes over environment verification tasks.
